</row>
<row valign="top">
<entry valign="top" align="left" namest="c1" nameend="c2"><emphasis effect="bold">Chapter Objectives:</emphasis>
<list id="fs-idm390680480" list-type="bulleted">
<item>Students will examine the ongoing debate about the scale and scope of the role of government by examining the conservative challenge to the New Deal liberal order.</item>
<item>Students will explain the causes of the end of the Cold War and ensuing changes and continuities in American foreign policy.</item>
<item>Students will explore the significant social and economic changes caused by deindustrialization, globalization, new technology, and the role of government.</item></list></entry>
</row>
